// =====================================================
// USAGE INSTRUCTIONS
// =====================================================
// 1. Apply to XAUUSD (Gold) chart on 5m, 15m, or 1h timeframe
// 2. Configure parameters in Settings panel:
//    - ZigZag Length: 9 (default) - adjust for market conditions
//    - Score Thresholds: Scalp=4, Intraday=5, Swing=6
